ragraph","text":"[I]这个批语写在中共中央办公厅信访处1972年5月编印的《要信摘报》第一—0号上。摘报说，一机部原副部长白坚的儿子白克功给毛主席写信，说白坚系陕西靖边县人，1926年参加革命。1968年在“文化大革命”中被隔离审查。白坚生前惠有高血压和冠状动脉硬化型心脏病，因得不到抢救在当年12月11日死于北京复兴医院。现在白坚已经死去4年了，但他的问题仍没有组织结论，家属在精神上、思想上负担很重，息请中央早日为他做出政治结论。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"d72ab83a6b","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":320,"end":320}},"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1c255d39b6","type":"paragraph","text":"送总理阅处。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d72ab83a6b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"82bd4ec478","type":"paragraph","text":"对反映白坚情况摘报的批语","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d72ab83a6b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8a4e50cf18","type":"title","text":"对反映白坚情况摘报的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d72ab83a6b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9268834afc","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d72ab83a6b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ac202bd7bd","type":"paragraph","text":"白坚在我的印象里不错，应为他做出政治结论。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d72ab83a6b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f8550f7079","type":"paragraph","text":"1972.05.31","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"d72ab83a6b","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}